    "text": "Social Security Benefit Payments Choice Act of 2021\n\nThis bill allows a\u00a0recipient of monthly Social Security benefits who does not concurrently receive Supplemental Security Income (SSI) to choose the day of the month that benefits are paid. SSI is a federal, needs-based program that provides cash benefits to older adults, blind individuals, and individuals with disabilities."
